<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>BunnyChat 🐰 | Teman Lucu Saat Sepi</title>

  <!-- Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&family=Sacramento&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    /* --- Global Style --- */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff5f9, #ffeaf4);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #444;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px 30px;
      background: url('https://i.ibb.co/GHdL9gZ/pastel-bg.png') repeat;
      background-size: 250px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #ffb6c1;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      color: #ff69b4;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px #fff;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #fffafa;
      border-radius: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.4);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* --- Profile Section (MODIFIED) --- */
    .profile {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* Lingkaran latar belakang */
    .profile-bg {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #fff 40%, #ffe6ef 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 170px;
      height: 170px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 25px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.6),
        0 0 50px rgba(255, 192, 203, 0.4),
        0 0 80px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Tulisan BunnyChat */
    .profile-name {
      font-family: 'Sacramento', cursive;
      font-size: 2.8em;
      color: #ff69b4;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 10px rgba(255, 192, 203, 0.8),
        0 0 20px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.6),
        0 0 30px rgba(255, 192, 203, 0.4);
      z-index: 2;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Efek bunga beterbangan */
    .flower {
      position: absolute;
      color: #ffb6c1;
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      animation: float 8s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
      50% { transform: translateY(-35px) rotate(45deg); opacity: 0.6; }
      100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(90deg); opacity: 1; }
    }

    .profile h2 {
      color: #ff69b4;
      margin: 20px 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.8em;
    }

    .profile p {
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #777;
    }

    /* --- Description Section --- */
    .description {
      margin-top: 35px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.8em;
      color: #555;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #ff69b4;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* --- Call To Action --- */
    .cta {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .cta button {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffb6c1, #ffa6c9);
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 35px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.5);
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,182,193,0.5); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255,182,193,0.7); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,182,193,0.5); }
    }

    .cta button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.07);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff8fb4, #ffb6c1);
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 25px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #777;
      background-color: #fff0f6;
      border-top: 2px solid #ffd1dc;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #ff69b4;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* --- Responsiveness --- */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2.2em;
      }

      .container {
        margin: 30px 15px;
        padding: 25px;
      }

      .description {
        text-align: left;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>🐰 BunnyChat</h1>
    <p>Teman lucu dan hangat untuk menemani hari-harimu yang sepi 💕</p>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="profile">
      <!-- Lingkaran profil berisi tulisan BunnyChat -->
      <div class="profile-bg">
        <div class="profile-name">BunnyChat</div>

        <!-- Banyak bunga beterbangan -->
        <div class="flower" style="top:15%; left:5%; animation-delay:0s;">🌸</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:60%; left:10%; animation-delay:1s;">🌷</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:70%; left:70%; animation-delay:2s;">💮</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:30%; left:80%; animation-delay:1.5s;">🌺</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:50%; left:40%; animation-delay:2.5s;">🌼</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:10%; left:50%; animation-delay:3s;">🌸</div>
        <div class="flower" style="top:75%; left:25%; animation-delay:1s;">🌷</div>
      </div>

      <h2>BunnyChat 🐰</h2>
      <p>Teman lucu dan hangat untuk menemani harimu yang sepi 🩷</p>
    </section>

    <section class="description">
      <p>
        Hai! Selamat datang di <span class="highlight">BunnyChat</span> 🐇  
        Tempat yang hangat dan penuh warna, di mana kamu bisa berbagi cerita, tawa, dan semangat baru.  
        Kami percaya bahwa setiap hari bisa menjadi indah kalau ada teman untuk berbagi 💫
      </p>
      <p>
        Di <strong>BunnyChat</strong>, kamu bisa:
      </p>
      <ul style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; margin-top:10px; color:#666; line-height:1.8em;">
        <li>🐰 Bertemu teman baru dengan minat yang sama</li>
        <li>💬 Berbagi cerita ringan dan lucu</li>
        <li>🌸 Menyebarkan semangat positif setiap hari</li>
        <li>🌷 Menemukan kehangatan di balik setiap obrolan</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:25px;">
        Yuk, jangan biarkan kesepian menghapus senyum manismu — karena BunnyChat selalu ada untukmu 🌼
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="cta">
      <button onclick="alert('🌸 Hai dari BunnyChat! Versi aplikasi segera hadir, ya 💖')">
        🌸 Gabung Sekarang 🌸
      </button>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 <a href="#">BunnyChat</a> 🩷 — Semua Hak Dilindungi</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
